  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'You want to know about the First Sundering.'
    nextOption: 'Yes.'
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'This Vale is built on its aftermath. The battle lasted eleven days. The Azure Veil''s founders performed the binding ritual on the twelfth — while the fighting was still ongoing.'
    nextOption: That worked?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'It worked well enough to last three centuries. The dragon was not killed. It was... paused. The founders knew the difference and chose not to explain it to their successors.'
    nextOption: Why not?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Because frightened soldiers fight harder when they believe the threat is eliminated. It is a reasonable tactical decision. It has some long-term drawbacks.'
    nextOption: Like the seal failing?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Like the seal failing. Yes.'
    nextOption: 
